high_descs: Turn around and walk to the edge of the counter, then turn right to face it.
Take the glass cup off of the counter.
Turn around and take one step, then turn around.
Put the glass cup on the second shelf to the left of the counter.
Turn right and and take three steps, then turn left to face the stove.
Open the microwave to take out the glass cup.
Turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn to the right.
Place the glass cup next to the other glass cup on the second shelf.
Turn around, go forward past the stove/oven, and turn right in front the white cabinet on the left of the stove/oven.
Pick up the glass cup from the far end of the cabinet top.
Turn around and face the shelf to the left of the white cabinet.
Place the glass cup on the shelf to the left of the white cabinet
Turn to your right, go forward, turn left to face the stove/cabinet, and look up the microwave above the stove/cabinet.
Open the microwave and take the cup glass out of it
Bring down the glass cup slowly and turn around, and go to the shelf.
Place the glass cup by the side of the first cup on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place two glass cups on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the very end of counter to your right and then turn right to face it.
Pick up the cup that's by the wall.
Take a step to your left to face the shelves.
Put the cup on the middle shelf to the right of it.
Turn right and walk to the stove and then face it.
Get the cup out of the microwave then close the microwave.
Walk back to where you put the first cup.
Put this cup to the left of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two cups on the shelf.
